            "description": "Logs out the currently authenticated user by invalidating the active session/token on the server.\n\n### Authentication\nThis endpoint requires an authenticated request.\n\n- Send the access token as a Bearer token.\n- The token value is stored in `{{token}}`.\n\nHeader format:\n```http\nAuthorization: Bearer {{token}}\n```\n\n### Required variables (environment: `al-madar-bank`)\n- `{{url}}` — Base API URL (e.g., `https://api.example.com`)\n- `{{token}}` — Current access token for the logged-in user\n\n### How to use\n1. Run **login** to obtain `{{token}}`.\n2. If `{{token}}` is expired, run **refresh** to update it.\n3. Send this **logout** request.\n\n### Expected responses\n- **200 OK** or **204 No Content** — Logout succeeded.\n- **401 Unauthorized** — Missing/invalid/expired token (authenticate again via **login** or update token via **refresh**)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
